66.meta_value: Atlas is the first modern platform that has lived up to its promise of lowering our developer costs.

65.meta_value: We were skeptical about Faust.js at first as we weren't sure WordPress could make a solid backend for a modern website. We were wrong. Faust.js and Atlas let us build exactly what we needed with modern tooling unencumbered by any WordPress or other limitations.
